---
const ctaPrimary = { label: "Zobacz realizacje", href: "/realizacje/" };
---

<section class="relative bg-black pb-24 pt-40 md:pb-34 md:pt-50 text-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-1/2 w-screen -translate-x-1/2 bg-black"></div>
  <div class="relative grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-center bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-gray-800 rounded-full px-4 py-0">
        <div class="flex text-orange-500 text-lg mr-2">
          ★★★★★
        </div>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">
          Ocena 5 / 5 <span class="text-gray-500 font-normal ml-1">10+ opinii</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8">
      Projektuje nowoczesne <br>
      <span class="text-white">strony internetowe</span>
    </h1>

      <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10">
        Kompleksowo prowadząt od strategii, przez design, po wdrożenie i wsparcie. Minimalistycznie,
        szybko i z myślą o wynikach.
      </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-8">
        <a class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition hover:brightness-95" href={ctaPrimary.href} title={ctaPrimary.label}>
          {ctaPrimary.label}
        </a>

      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="flex -space-x-3 mr-4">
          <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-black object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=1" alt="User">
          <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-black object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=2" alt="User">
          <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-black object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=3" alt="User">
          <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-black object-cover" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=4" alt="User">
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">40+</span>
          zadowolonych <br>klientów
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 sm:p-6">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-200">Najczęściej wybierane</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
          <span>Strony dla firm i marek osobistych</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
          <span>Sklepy online gotowe do skalowania</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
          <span>Opieka i rozwoj stron po wdrożeniu</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
          <span>Kampanie reklamowe w Google ADS</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)]"></span>
          <span>Landing page pod kampanie i leady</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Przejrzysty proces</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Stala komunikacja, jasne etapy i pelna opieka od briefu po wsparcie po wdrożeniu.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
